# One package name per line. Blank lines and lines starting with `#`
# are ignored. The bundler resolves the transitive Imports / Depends /
# LinkingTo closure for each entry — you do NOT need to list deps.
#
# Optional `==<version>` suffix is recognised but currently advisory:
# the bundler always pulls the latest version compatible with the
# requested R minor. The lockfile (manifest.json) records what
# actually shipped.

ggplot2
dplyr
data.table
testthat

